column4: hi, im currently stuck in uname (command line) how do i exit uname please
that the uname command got stuck?
what do I press to get out of it
what did you type, exactly? just 'uname<enter>' or any flags?
it should go right back to the commandline prompt already
can you open a new terminal?
k, now type:  ps axf | grep uname
I worked out what I had to do, just press "q"
